# Coursera submission artifacts

Add your real Coursera/OpenShift evidence here before submitting.

Required files:

1. `oc-pipelines-console-pvc-details.png`
2. `github-actions-success.txt`
3. `oc-pipelines-oc-final.png`
4. `oc-pipelines-oc-green.png`
5. `openshift-app-logs.txt`

Do not use fake screenshots. Use the real screenshots and terminal output from your own GitHub Actions and OpenShift cluster.
